## Internal Instructions (English)

- Apply full TDD for new features, bug fixes, Server Actions, Route Handlers, and business logic—not for pure style or config-only edits.
- Prefer Vitest co-located tests; Playwright E2E for critical flows only; use MSW for fetch from client components, `vi.mock` for direct action/handler tests.
- For end-to-end automation of the cycle, delegate to the **`tdd` subagent**; this rule documents policy and structure.

